h: 100%; height: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//static.showit.co/800/mfwQae1NFVPkuQQXAgMXSA/shared/photo-50.jpg&quot;);" data-img="about-cassandra_3" class="se-img se-gr slzy"><span role="img" aria-label="A close up photo of a white and green wedding bouquet "></span></div><noscript><img src="//static.showit.co/400/mfwQae1NFVPkuQQXAgMXSA/shared/photo-50.jpg" class="se-img" alt="A close up photo of a white and green wedding bouquet " title="bridal-bouquet-wedding"/></noscript></div><div data-sid="about-cassandra_4" class="sie-about-cassandra_4 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><h2 class="se-t sie-about-cassandra_4-text st-m-heading st-d-heading se-rc">about<br>Nandon Klinton&nbsp;<br></h2></div><div data-sid="about-cassandra_5" class="sie-about-cassandra_5 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><h3 class="se-t sie-about-cassandra_5-text st-m-heading st-d-heading se-rc">With a talent for capturing the unseen and the unfiltered, Nandon Klinton strips back the layers to reveal love in its truest form: effortless, sophisticated, and unforgettable.<br></h3></div><div data-sid="about-cassandra_6" class="sie-about-cassandra_6 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-about-cassandra_6-text st-m-paragraph st-d-paragraph se-rc">Recognised by her iconic style, Nandon Klinton is a photographic artist fluent in the language of storytelling. Creating beautiful imagery for over 15 years, for both couples and creatives in Australia and across the globe.<br><br>Nandon Klinton is best known for her honest and timeless photography style. With a unique talent for encompassing raw emotion in a frame, hypnotised by the romance of modern lovers she captures moments unseen, effortlessly. Seamless in her execution, she leads with a sophistication of composition, stripping back the layers and capturing<br>the real and the unfiltered.<br><br>With each moment in time mesmerising to relive, Nandon Klinton’s expertise is in the details. Creating a visual story weaved from the truly intimate and celebratory moments. Fleeting seconds with the bride, realising the weight of her next few steps, to a mother’s hand<br>squeezed in excitement, a grooms celebration strolling back down the aisle with his love. The outcome is incomparable, painting a picture so vivid for a couple to forever hold.<br><br>Nandon Klinton finds herself most inspired when capturing a love that sets every heart in the room alight, leaving you with a visual portrayal of the unparalleled love shared between souls. Truth lives in each frame, your story told in its most crushingly beautiful form.<br><br></p></div><a href="/contact" target="_self" class="sie-about-cassandra_7 se" data-sid="about-cassandra_7" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><span type="button" aria-label="Contact Nandon Klinton" class="se-button st-primary" data-link="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;page&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;contact&quot;}"><span class="st-m-primary st-d-primary">Contact Nandon Klinton</span></span></a></div></div></div><div id="featured" data-bid="featured" class="sb sib-featured" style="height: 456px;"><div class="ss-s ss-bg"><div class="sc" style="width:1200px"><div data-sid="featured_2" class="sie-featured_2 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//static.showit.co/1200/nOym1zZfaObZlzmJkUtH3Q/shared/vogue-logo.png&quot;);" data-img="featured_2" class="se-img se-gr slzy"><span role="img" aria-label="Vogue Australia Logo for the as featured in section of the homepage "></span></div><noscript><img src="//static.showit.co/400/nOym1zZfaObZlzmJkUtH3Q/shared/vogue-logo.png" class="se-img" alt="Vogue Australia Logo for the as featured in section of the homepage " title="Vogue-logo"/></noscript></div><div data-sid="featured_3" class="sie-featured_3 se" styl